name: number->string
description:
Convert a number to a string in base <radix> (defaults to 10).
<radix> must be between <*min-radix*> and <*max-radix*>.
Returns #f if failed coercion.

name: string->number
description:
Convert a string to a number in base <radix> (defaults to 10).
<radix> must be between <*min-radix*> and <*max-radix*>.
Returns #f if failed coercion.

name: keyword->symbol
description: Convert a keyword to a symbol.

name: symbol->keyword
description: Convert a symbol to a keyword.

name: string->symbol
description: Convert a string to a symbol.

name: symbol->string
description: Convert a symbol to a string.

name: string->keyword
description: Convert a string to a keyword.

name: keyword->string
description: Convert a keyword to a string.
